Rating: 1
Blah. The bourbon is nearly imperceptible. The texture is mush. The flavor is like cream and yams. Ho-hum.

Rating: 2
I had my eye on this recipe for thanksgiving. It was moist and pleasant, but nothing special. I made half the amount listed here, but still used the full 2 tablespoons of bourbon, and STILL couldn't taste it in the final results. I think there have to be more interesting ways to fix sweet potatoes. But again, if you are a big fan of sweet potatoes, you may well love how moist these are.